description: Regulus Resources Inc. operates as a mineral exploration company. Its flagship project is the AntaKori copper-gold-silver project comprises 20 mineral concessions that cover an area of 438 hectares located in the Yanacocha-Hualgayoc mining district in the Department of Cajamarca, Northern Peru. Regulus Resources Inc. was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
ceo: Mr. John E. Black B.Sc., B.Sc. M.Sc., M.Sc.
